{"tid":837432,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中秋節燒死左人 點算","createTime":"2018-09-26T11:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T12:45:13.000Z","uid":152147,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"00d3dac0b912c20892fff0c207faa0cf70335a79","tid":837432,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"話說我地朋友圈入面有個叫呀雞 佢成撚日屌人老母 又串 把口又衰 咁個次我地係房到恰鳩個呀叔啦 呀雞條仆街竟然叫佢呀叔報驚 一啲雷氣都冇 我真係屌你老母呀 我大王最撚憎啲25仔㗎啦 就決定比啲顏色佢<br />\n咁中秋節個日 我call齊班友 呀雞佢又真係上埋黎 咁我地就一人做佢幾獲啦 做到差唔多 咁都係我時候啦 順便試下可唔可以一腳踏飛佢<br />\n一踏 呀屌 飛唔起嘅 咪捉住佢再踏過 點撚知都唔得 嬲嬲地就去左屌呀儀<br />\n點撚知屌完番到黎 呀雞死左 咁我身為大佬 梗係唔可以劣 我劣一劣條鳩 就同幾個弟兄夾手夾腳買齊野燒左佢 <br />\n而家燒就燒完啦 變左火雞 但個心好驚 點算"},{"pid":"55f53ee84a974c4f033055f2df18f1cbd1f68f8c","tid":837432,"uid":184509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:18:21.000Z","msg":"呢度冇人識你喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7452d424047bf56e1608431af59302e560fa7e","tid":837432,"uid":41915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/191827_e681b4ff442d7649ee1d386b58858a10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F191827_e681b4ff442d7649ee1d386b58858a10.png&h=d973feba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a0732d492f82405a6c3263ef949ca6525120f6b","tid":837432,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:18:34.000Z","msg":"叫神仙B幫你"},{"pid":"69cc0c43cd4cabd51a5daa9ac5c01e44ed5b83c4","tid":837432,"uid":139617,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"唔好去自首 你班朋友唔敢篤你出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d530a4d5ece736f1a604f861e49950de5a95901","tid":837432,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"咪跟梁蛇叫下雞咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"